 The man was found face down, tangled in the reeds metres from the low water bridge used daily by passersby. The cause of the man’s death is still unknown and his identity could not be confirmed. The Middelburg Fire Brigade retrieved the corpse from the river. •Police have opened an inquest docket.   Kry nuus op ’n drafstap. Stoor ons bystand nommer (072 248 3855) op jou foon, stuur ’n WhatsApp boodskap met die woorde “Add me” om nuusflits skakels op jou foon te kry.”